l consortia's school improvement functions, and to what extent it varied by region?&#10;Speaker: Kirsty Williams AM&#10;Content: I think it's fair to say that, on occasion, I have received feedback that there was a conflict between what was going on at an individual school under the school improvement programme and whether, then, they welcomed support from the regional consortia as part of that. So, in some cases, if we're being absolutely honest, there">
