l &quot;deep-dive discussion&quot; about the factors influencing student performance in her department. This suggests that there is an understanding of the need to investigate and understand various elements affecting student achievement better, including socioeconomic backgrounds and school-specific factors.&#10;&#10;In summary, while Kirsty Williams does not provide a specific reason for the increase in children on free school meals who did not reach Level 2+ in 2016, she alludes to unusual circumstances, differences among schools, and the importance of deeper analysis to understand contributing factors better.">
