ust before exams.&#10;&#10;Therefore, to improve the effectiveness of PDG usage, there needs to be a focus on leadership development, strategic use of PDG, and early intervention. Additionally, there should be measures in place to demonstrate that PDG is being used properly and that good practice is being shared across regions. The new PDG regional advisers are expected to play a crucial role in this regard.">
