pplied those lessons to the wider school improvement agenda. However, she acknowledges the value of ongoing dialogue with people involved in the program and considers developing a Welsh toolkit around good practice, evidence base, and research. Therefore, there is a possibility for Professor Ainscow to provide further input to the Welsh Government on this matter, especially if he has additional insights that can help improve recruitment and diversity within the regional consortia.">
